english.INCLUDE_CONDITIONS_BANNED_IN_ROULETTE_RI: Include Conditions Banned in Roulette Rivals
english.UI_ROULETTE_PLAYING_CARD_HACKER_DESC: A sharpened custom playing card marked with a reminder of the past. Great for throwing, and accessing off-limits areas.
english.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DESC: For an explosive game of poker. This inconspicuous poker chip is sure to attract casual attention, and can be remotely detonated to blow doors open. Relatively quiet.
english.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DETONATOR_DES: A remote trigger device, used to detonate an Explosive Poker Chip.
english.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_DESCRIPTION:
This will regenerate Random Roulette Contracts with a random seed. This will not regenerate Trilogy Roulette Contracts.
USING THIS IN A TRILOGY ROULETTE CONTRACT WILL CAUSE AN ERROR.
english.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: A golden variant of the Custom 5mm fit for a glamorous night at the casino. Designed to pass through frisks, this weapon utilizes wall-piercing ammunition.
english.firearms_hero_icer_desc: A magnum pistol modified to shoot Instant Concussion Rounds. Low rate of fire and non-lethal.
english.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: An airsoft rifle modified to shoot up to six sedative darts. Magazine fed, featuring a classic blue finish with premium iron sights and a state-of-the-art tracer.
english.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: Show them true efficiency with this modern Japanese get-up: the classic black, red and white color scheme with safety glasses, gloves and a communicator is sure to prove how serious you are.
english.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
english.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: 47 has started his ICA Entrance test by the Tool Shed.
english.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
english.ui_starting_location_polar_test_gates_de: 47 Has approached the front gate, hidden in shadow.
english.APC_desc: 47 has infiltrated the train undetected, now disguised as the Train Conductor, ready to confront the Constant.
english.office_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Office Closet for 47 to use.
english.workbench_desc: Diana has smuggled a item underneath the weapon workbench for for 47 to use.
english.storage_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Storage Car infront of the Ether Lab Car for 47 to use.
english.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: Show them all what a high roller you are with this exclusive waistcoat. Features driving gloves, black slacks, shoes and shirt, with a glittering red vest.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: One Elimination type and two Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: Two Elimination types and one Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: Only one Elimination type and Disguise type required for Mission completion.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: No Elimination methods required for Mission completion.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: No Disguises required for Mission completion.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: If 47 is frisked, the Mission will fail.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: Assassinate all Targets, Assassinate all Witnesses and do it all in your suit.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: 47 must steal a semi-auto pistol from a guard.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RAT_DESC: 47 must steal a tube of rat poison.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: 47 must steal a key, a keycard, a security access drive or a RFID chip.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: If any accident kill/pacifcation bodies are found, 47 will have 4 minutes to complete the mission.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: 47 starts the Mission a little buzzed. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: 47 wakes up after drinking too much alcohol. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated. If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated, 47 must not change out of his suit.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: If any shot misses or is not a headshot, the mission will instantly fail. If 47 moves on red, the game will instantly fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: If any shot misses, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: If any shot that hits a npc is not a headshot, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: Do not Eliminate/Pacify when the light is Blue/Red
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: If 47 moves while the light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_TITLE: Do not move when the light is Red
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: If 47 is spotted, any witnesses must be eliminated.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
47 has 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in 47's path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives. A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: If a door is unlocked you will have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: If you Trespass you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: Flamingo suit only, Eliminate all targets, If recorded, evidence must be deleted. Finish Mission in 10 minutes.
english.UUI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OBJ_FLAMINGO: Delete evidence from the Hunting Cameras
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: 47 starts visibly armed. 20 Non-targets must be Eliminated, NPCs must stay Alerted and all Targets must be Eliminated. Suit Only.
english.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE: The Set Seed field can be used to set the seed for both Roulette modes.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: Complete the Mission in your starting Disguise.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_TITLE: Do not change your starting Disguise
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
No bodies may be found, no non-targets may be Eliminated.
You may not be seen and you must destroy any Surveillance recordings if recorded.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STALKER_OBJ_2: Do not touch the Phantom's Aura
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: Eliminate all Targets by any methods you deem fit.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
If NPCs are not currently Alerted or Panicked, a one minute timer will start.
You must increase tension to stop the timer or fail the mission.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: If NPCs are Alerted or in a Combat Situation, you must de-escalate the situation in 90 seconds or fail the mission.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: If NPCs are Alerted you must de-escalate within 90 seconds
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Complete the mission within 10 minutes, or fail.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: Do not change disguise more than twice.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: Do not change disguise more than twice
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_DESC:
You have 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in your path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_FAIL: Time is relative to the observer. When you're looking down the barrel of a gun time slows down, your whole life flashes by. Stay with it, and you can live a lifetime in that split second.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_DESC: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Guards. Non-Target Civilian Eliminations are allowed.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_TITLE: Do not Eliminate Non Target Guards
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COVERT_ASSASSIN_D: If you are detected you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SLOW_AND_STEADY_D: If you use Agility you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_KIL: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Civilians. Non-Target Guard Eliminations are allowed.
english.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_TIT: Do not Eliminate Non Target Civilians

french.INCLUDE_SPECIFIC_MELEE_WEAPONS: Inclus une arme de mêlée spécifique
french.INCLUDE_SPECIFIC_FIREARMS: Inclus une arme à feu spécifique
french.INCLUDE_SPECIFIC_ACCIDENTS_POISON_KILLS: Inclus un accident spécifique / poison spécifique
french.INCLUDE_CONDITIONS_BANNED_IN_ROULETTE_RI: Inclus les conditions bannies du Roulette Rivals
french.UI_ROULETTE_PLAYING_CARD_HACKER_DESC: Une carte à jouer personnalisée et aiguisée, marquée d'un rappel du passé. Idéale pour les lancers et l'accès aux zones interdites.
french.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DESC: Pour une partie de poker explosive. Ce jeton de poker discret ne manquera pas d'attirer l'attention et peut être déclenché à distance pour faire sauter des portes. Relativement silencieux.
french.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DETONATOR_DES: Dispositif de déclenchement à distance, utilisé pour faire exploser un jeton de poker explosif.
french.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_DESCRIPTION:
Cela régénérera les contrats de roulette aléatoire avec une seed aléatoire. Cela ne régénère pas les contrats de roulette trilogique.
L'UTILISATION DE CELA DANS UN CONTRAT ROULETTE TRILOGIE CAUSERA UNE ERREUR.
french.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_TITLE: Régénérer les contrats de roulette aléatoire ?
french.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: Une variante dorée du Custom 5mm pour une nuit glamour au casino. Conçue pour passer les fouilles, cette arme utilise des munitions perforantes.
french.UI_MENU_PAGE_REGEN_CONTRACTS: Régénérer les contrats de roulette aléatoires
french.firearms_hero_icer_desc: Un pistolet magnum modifié pour tirer des balles à commotion instantanée. Faible cadence de tir et non létal.
french.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: Un fusil airsoft modifié pour tirer jusqu'à six fléchettes sédatives. Alimenté par un chargeur, il est doté d'une finition bleue classique, d'une lunette de visée haut de gamme et d'un traceur ultramoderne.
french.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: Montrez-leur à quel point vous êtes un flambeur grâce à ce gilet exclusif. Il comprend des gants de conduite, un pantalon, des chaussures et une chemise noirs, ainsi qu'un gilet rouge scintillant.
french.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: Montrez-leur votre efficacité avec ce costume japonais à la fois traditionnel et moderne. Avec ses couleurs classiques noir, rouge et blanc, ses lunettes de sécurité, ses gants et son communicateur, vous leur montrerez à quel point vous êtes sérieux.
french.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: Je suis presque sûr que cela provoque un paradoxe temporel.
french.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: 47 commence son test d'entrée à l'ICA, à la remise à outils
french.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: Je suis presque sûr que cela provoque un paradoxe temporel.
french.ui_starting_location_polar_test_gates_de: 47 s'est approché du portail d'entrée, caché dans l'ombre.
french.APC_desc: 47 s'est infiltré dans le train sans se faire repérer, déguisé en conducteur de train, prêt à affronter le Constant.
french.office_desc: Diana a introduit clandestinement un objet dans le placard du bureau pour que 47 puisse l'utiliser.
french.workbench_desc: Diana a dissimulé un objet sous l'établi d'armes pour que 47 puisse l'utiliser.
french.storage_desc: Diana a introduit clandestinement un objet dans le wagon de stockage situé devant le wagon du laboratoire d'éther pour que 47 puisse l'utiliser.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: Un objectif de type élimination et deux objectifs de type déguisement requis pour l'achèvement de la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: Deux types d'élimination et un type de déguisement Objectifs requis pour l'accomplissement de la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: Un seul type d'élimination et un seul type de déguisement sont nécessaires pour terminer la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: Aucune méthode d'élimination n'est nécessaire pour terminer la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: Aucun déguisement n'est nécessaire pour terminer la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: Si 47 est fouillé, la mission échouera.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: Éliminez toutes les cibles par des tirs à la tête, éliminez tous les témoins et faites tout cela dans votre costume.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_TITLE: Éliminez toutes les cibles par des tirs à la tête
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: 47 doit voler un pistolet semi-auto à un garde
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RAT_DESC: 47 doit voler un tube de mort aux rats.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RAT_TITLE: Volez de la mort aux rats
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: 47 doit voler une clé, une carte d'accès, un disque de dur de sécurité ou une puce d'identification.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: Si des corps tués par accident/pacification sont trouvés, 47 disposera de 4 minutes pour terminer la mission.
Aucun corps lié à un accident/pacification ne doit trainer
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: 47 démarre la mission, un peu perdu.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER: Boire ou Éliminer, il faut choisir
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: 47 se réveille après avoir un peu trop bu.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_VANISHER_DESCRIPT: Cachez tous les corps en 90 secondes.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: 47 commence avec rien d'autre que sa tenue. Toutes les cibles doivent être éliminées. Si 47 élimine un pnjs alors que la lumière est bleue ou pacifie un PNJ alors que la lumière est rouge, la mission échoue.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: 47 commence avec rien d'autre que sa tenue. Toutes les cibles doivent être éliminées, 47 ne doit pas se changer.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: Si un tir manque ou n'est pas un tir de tête, la mission échoue instantanément. Si 47 est blessé, la mission échoue instantanément.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES: Une balle retrouve forcément sa destination
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: Si un tir est raté, il ne restera que quatre minutes pour atteindre tous les objectifs.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: Si les tirs qui touchent un pnj ne sont pas des tirs de tête, il ne restera plus que quatre minutes pour atteindre tous les objectifs.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: Si 47 élimine un PNJ alors que la lumière est bleue ou pacifie un pnjs alors que la lumière est rouge, la mission échouera.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: Ne pas éliminer/pacifier lorsque la lumière est bleue/rouge
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: Si 47 bouge pendant que la lumière est rouge, la mission échouera instantanément.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_TITLE: Ne pas bouger lorsque la lumière est rouge
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: Si 47 est repéré, tout témoin doit être éliminé.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
47 a 1 minute pour accomplir la mission.
Gagnez du temps en apaisant et en éliminant tous ceux qui se trouvent sur le chemin de 47.
Pour sauver votre peau, vous devez remplir tous les autres objectifs. Un dangereux fantôme traque 47 à travers le niveau.
Si vous entrez dans son aura ou si vous tentez de l'éliminer ou de l'apaiser, vous échouerez instantanément la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: Si une porte est déverrouillée, vous disposerez de 4 minutes pour atteindre tous les objectifs.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_TITLE: Ne pas déverrouiller une seule porte
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: En cas d'intrusion, vous disposez de 4 minutes pour atteindre tous les objectifs.
Ne pas s'introduire dans un lieu interdit
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_EYESEEA: On dit au revoir à la vue
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PLACATION_DESC: Pacifiez trois pnjs sans être remarqué.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PLACATION_TITLE: Pacifiez trois pnjs sans être remarqué
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: Combinaison de flamant rose uniquement, éliminer toutes les cibles, si vous êtes filmé, les preuves doivent être effacées. Terminer la mission en 10 minutes.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Migrez vers le sud en 10 minutes
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: 47 commence visiblement armé. 20 non cibles doivent être éliminées, les pnjs doivent rester alertes et toutes les cibles doivent être éliminées. Tenue de départ uniquement.
french.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE:
The Set Seed field can be used to set the seed, numerical values only.
If you wish to save a contract, you must use this command:
/save seedhere missionidhere
This is case sensitive. The following are valid missionIds:
Showstopper
WoT
Icon
Landslide
Author
Gilded
Sand

SitusInversus

french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: 47 commence avec rien d'autre que sa tenue. Toutes les cibles doivent être éliminées.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: Complètez la mission dans votre costume de départ.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_TITLE: Ne pas changez votre costume de départ
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
Aucun corps ne peut être trouvé, aucune cible ne peut être éliminée.
Vous ne pouvez pas être vu et vous devez détruire tout enregistrement de surveillance.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
Un dangereux fantôme traverse le niveau.
Si vous entrez dans son aura ou si vous tentez de l'éliminer ou de l'apaiser, vous échouerez instantanément la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: Éliminez les cibles de la façon dont vous souhaitez.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
Si les pnjs ne sont pas en état d'alerte ou de panique, un compte à rebours d'une minute démarre.
Vous devez augmenter la tension pour arrêter le chronomètre ou échouer la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_TITLE: Gardez la pression/tension sur les npcs
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: Si des pnjs sont alertés ou en situation de combat, vous devez désamorcer la situation en 90 secondes ou échouer la mission.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: Si des pnjs sont alertés, vous devez désamorcer la situation dans les 90 secondes.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Terminez la mission en moins de 10 minutes, ou échouez.
Terminez la mission en moins de 10 minutes
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: Ne pas changer de déguisement plus de deux fois.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: Ne pas changer de déguisement plus de deux fois
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_DESC:
Vous avez 1 minute pour accomplir la mission.
Gagnez du temps en pacifiant et en éliminant tous ceux qui se trouvent sur votre chemin.
Pour vous sauver, vous devez remplir tous les autres objectifs.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_FAIL: Le temps est relatif à l'observateur. Lorsque vous regardez le canon d'une arme à feu, le temps ralentit et votre vie entière défile. Restez dans le coup et vous pourrez vivre toute une vie en une fraction de seconde.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_DESC: Ne pas éliminer les gardes non ciblés. Les éliminations de civils non ciblés sont autorisées.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_TITLE: Ne pas éliminer les gardes non ciblés
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COVERT_ASSASSIN_D: Si vous êtes détecté, vous disposez de 4 minutes pour atteindre tous les objectifs.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SLOW_AND_STEADY_D: Si vous utilisez l'Agilité, vous disposez de 4 minutes pour atteindre tous les objectifs.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_KIL: Ne pas éliminer les civils non ciblés. Les éliminations de gardes non ciblés sont autorisées.
french.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_TIT: Ne pas éliminer les civils non ciblés

italian.UI_ROULETTE_PLAYING_CARD_HACKER_DESC: A sharpened custom playing card marked with a reminder of the past. Great for throwing, and accessing off-limits areas.
italian.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DESC: For an explosive game of poker. This inconspicuous poker chip is sure to attract casual attention, and can be remotely detonated to blow doors open. Relatively quiet.
italian.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DETONATOR_DES: A remote trigger device, used to detonate an Explosive Poker Chip.
italian.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_DESCRIPTION:
This will regenerate Random Roulette Contracts with a random seed. This will not regenerate Trilogy Roulette Contracts.
USING THIS IN A TRILOGY ROULETTE CONTRACT WILL CAUSE AN ERROR.
italian.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: A golden variant of the Custom 5mm fit for a glamorous night at the casino. Designed to pass through frisks, this weapon utilizes wall-piercing ammunition.
italian.firearms_hero_icer_desc: A magnum pistol modified to shoot Instant Concussion Rounds. Low rate of fire and non-lethal.
italian.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: An airsoft rifle modified to shoot up to six sedative darts. Magazine fed, featuring a classic blue finish with premium iron sights and a state-of-the-art tracer.
italian.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: Show them true efficiency with this modern Japanese get-up: the classic black, red and white color scheme with safety glasses, gloves and a communicator is sure to prove how serious you are.
italian.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
italian.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: 47 has started his ICA Entrance test by the Tool Shed.
italian.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
italian.ui_starting_location_polar_test_gates_de: 47 Has approached the front gate, hidden in shadow.
italian.APC_desc: 47 has infiltrated the train undetected, now disguised as the Train Conductor, ready to confront the Constant.
italian.office_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Office Closet for 47 to use.
italian.workbench_desc: Diana has smuggled a item underneath the weapon workbench for for 47 to use.
italian.storage_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Storage Car infront of the Ether Lab Car for 47 to use.
italian.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: Show them all what a high roller you are with this exclusive waistcoat. Features driving gloves, black slacks, shoes and shirt, with a glittering red vest.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: One Elimination type and two Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: Two Elimination types and one Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: Only one Elimination type and Disguise type required for Mission completion.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: No Elimination methods required for Mission completion.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: No Disguises required for Mission completion.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: If 47 is frisked, the Mission will fail.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: Assassinate all Targets, Assassinate all Witnesses and do it all in your suit.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: 47 must steal a semi-auto pistol from a guard.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RAT_DESC: 47 must steal a tube of rat poison.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: 47 must steal a key, a keycard, a security access drive or a RFID chip.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: If any accident kill/pacifcation bodies are found, 47 will have 4 minutes to complete the mission.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: 47 starts the Mission a little buzzed. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: 47 wakes up after drinking too much alcohol. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated. If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated, 47 must not change out of his suit.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: If any shot misses or is not a headshot, the mission will instantly fail. If 47 moves on red, the game will instantly fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: If any shot misses, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: If any shot that hits a npc is not a headshot, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: Do not Eliminate/Pacify when the light is Blue/Red
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: If 47 moves while the light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_TITLE: Do not move when the light is Red
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: If 47 is spotted, any witnesses must be eliminated.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
47 has 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in 47's path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives. A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: If a door is unlocked you will have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: If you Trespass you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: Flamingo suit only, Eliminate all targets, If recorded, evidence must be deleted. Finish Mission in 10 minutes.
italian.UUI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OBJ_FLAMINGO: Delete evidence from the Hunting Cameras
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: 47 starts visibly armed. 20 Non-targets must be Eliminated, NPCs must stay Alerted and all Targets must be Eliminated. Suit Only.
italian.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE: The Set Seed field can be used to set the seed for both Roulette modes.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: Complete the Mission in your starting Disguise.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_TITLE: Do not change your starting Disguise
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
No bodies may be found, no non-targets may be Eliminated.
You may not be seen and you must destroy any Surveillance recordings if recorded.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STALKER_OBJ_2: Do not touch the Phantom's Aura
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: Eliminate all Targets by any methods you deem fit.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
If NPCs are not currently Alerted or Panicked, a one minute timer will start.
You must increase tension to stop the timer or fail the mission.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: If NPCs are Alerted or in a Combat Situation, you must de-escalate the situation in 90 seconds or fail the mission.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: If NPCs are Alerted you must de-escalate within 90 seconds
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Complete the mission within 10 minutes, or fail.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: Do not change disguise more than twice.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: Do not change disguise more than twice
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_DESC:
You have 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in your path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_FAIL: Time is relative to the observer. When you're looking down the barrel of a gun time slows down, your whole life flashes by. Stay with it, and you can live a lifetime in that split second.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_DESC: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Guards. Non-Target Civilian Eliminations are allowed.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_TITLE: Do not Eliminate Non Target Guards
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COVERT_ASSASSIN_D: If you are detected you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SLOW_AND_STEADY_D: If you use Agility you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_KIL: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Civilians. Non-Target Guard Eliminations are allowed.
italian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_TIT: Do not Eliminate Non Target Civilians
italian.RR_KILLCONDITION_UNARMED_DESC: Eliminate a Target with a Neck Snap.
italian.RR_KILLCONDITION_AR_UNSILENCED: Eliminate Target with Unsilenced Assault Rifle

italian.RR_KILLCONDITION_AR_SILENCED_DESC: Eliminate a Target with a Assault Rifle.

german.INCLUDE_CONDITIONS_BANNED_IN_ROULETTE_RI: Include Conditions Banned in Roulette Rivals
german.UI_ROULETTE_PLAYING_CARD_HACKER_DESC: A sharpened custom playing card marked with a reminder of the past. Great for throwing, and accessing off-limits areas.
german.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DESC: For an explosive game of poker. This inconspicuous poker chip is sure to attract casual attention, and can be remotely detonated to blow doors open. Relatively quiet.
german.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DETONATOR_DES: A remote trigger device, used to detonate an Explosive Poker Chip.
german.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_DESCRIPTION:
This will regenerate Random Roulette Contracts with a random seed. This will not regenerate Trilogy Roulette Contracts.
USING THIS IN A TRILOGY ROULETTE CONTRACT WILL CAUSE AN ERROR.
german.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: A golden variant of the Custom 5mm fit for a glamorous night at the casino. Designed to pass through frisks, this weapon utilizes wall-piercing ammunition.
german.firearms_hero_icer_desc: A magnum pistol modified to shoot Instant Concussion Rounds. Low rate of fire and non-lethal.
german.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: An airsoft rifle modified to shoot up to six sedative darts. Magazine fed, featuring a classic blue finish with premium iron sights and a state-of-the-art tracer.
german.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: Show them true efficiency with this modern Japanese get-up: the classic black, red and white color scheme with safety glasses, gloves and a communicator is sure to prove how serious you are.
german.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
german.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: 47 has started his ICA Entrance test by the Tool Shed.
german.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
german.ui_starting_location_polar_test_gates_de: 47 Has approached the front gate, hidden in shadow.
german.APC_desc: 47 has infiltrated the train undetected, now disguised as the Train Conductor, ready to confront the Constant.
german.office_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Office Closet for 47 to use.
german.workbench_desc: Diana has smuggled a item underneath the weapon workbench for for 47 to use.
german.storage_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Storage Car infront of the Ether Lab Car for 47 to use.
german.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: Show them all what a high roller you are with this exclusive waistcoat. Features driving gloves, black slacks, shoes and shirt, with a glittering red vest.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: One Elimination type and two Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: Two Elimination types and one Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: Only one Elimination type and Disguise type required for Mission completion.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: No Elimination methods required for Mission completion.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: No Disguises required for Mission completion.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: If 47 is frisked, the Mission will fail.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: Assassinate all Targets, Assassinate all Witnesses and do it all in your suit.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: 47 must steal a semi-auto pistol from a guard.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RAT_DESC: 47 must steal a tube of rat poison.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: 47 must steal a key, a keycard, a security access drive or a RFID chip.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: If any accident kill/pacifcation bodies are found, 47 will have 4 minutes to complete the mission.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: 47 starts the Mission a little buzzed. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: 47 wakes up after drinking too much alcohol. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated. If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated, 47 must not change out of his suit.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: If any shot misses or is not a headshot, the mission will instantly fail. If 47 moves on red, the game will instantly fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: If any shot misses, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: If any shot that hits a npc is not a headshot, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: Do not Eliminate/Pacify when the light is Blue/Red
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: If 47 moves while the light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_TITLE: Do not move when the light is Red
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: If 47 is spotted, any witnesses must be eliminated.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
47 has 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in 47's path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives. A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: If a door is unlocked you will have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: If you Trespass you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: Flamingo suit only, Eliminate all targets, If recorded, evidence must be deleted. Finish Mission in 10 minutes.
german.UUI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OBJ_FLAMINGO: Delete evidence from the Hunting Cameras
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: 47 starts visibly armed. 20 Non-targets must be Eliminated, NPCs must stay Alerted and all Targets must be Eliminated. Suit Only.
german.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE: The Set Seed field can be used to set the seed for both Roulette modes.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: Complete the Mission in your starting Disguise.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_TITLE: Do not change your starting Disguise
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
No bodies may be found, no non-targets may be Eliminated.
You may not be seen and you must destroy any Surveillance recordings if recorded.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STALKER_OBJ_2: Do not touch the Phantom's Aura
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: Eliminate all Targets by any methods you deem fit.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
If NPCs are not currently Alerted or Panicked, a one minute timer will start.
You must increase tension to stop the timer or fail the mission.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: If NPCs are Alerted or in a Combat Situation, you must de-escalate the situation in 90 seconds or fail the mission.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: If NPCs are Alerted you must de-escalate within 90 seconds
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Complete the mission within 10 minutes, or fail.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: Do not change disguise more than twice.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: Do not change disguise more than twice
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_DESC:
You have 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in your path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_FAIL: Time is relative to the observer. When you're looking down the barrel of a gun time slows down, your whole life flashes by. Stay with it, and you can live a lifetime in that split second.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_DESC: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Guards. Non-Target Civilian Eliminations are allowed.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_TITLE: Do not Eliminate Non Target Guards
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COVERT_ASSASSIN_D: If you are detected you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SLOW_AND_STEADY_D: If you use Agility you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_KIL: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Civilians. Non-Target Guard Eliminations are allowed.
german.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_TIT: Do not Eliminate Non Target Civilians

spanish.UI_ROULETTE_PLAYING_CARD_HACKER_DESC: A sharpened custom playing card marked with a reminder of the past. Great for throwing, and accessing off-limits areas.
spanish.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DESC: For an explosive game of poker. This inconspicuous poker chip is sure to attract casual attention, and can be remotely detonated to blow doors open. Relatively quiet.
spanish.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DETONATOR_DES: A remote trigger device, used to detonate an Explosive Poker Chip.
spanish.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_DESCRIPTION:
This will regenerate Random Roulette Contracts with a random seed. This will not regenerate Trilogy Roulette Contracts.
USING THIS IN A TRILOGY ROULETTE CONTRACT WILL CAUSE AN ERROR.
spanish.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: A golden variant of the Custom 5mm fit for a glamorous night at the casino. Designed to pass through frisks, this weapon utilizes wall-piercing ammunition.
spanish.firearms_hero_icer_desc: A magnum pistol modified to shoot Instant Concussion Rounds. Low rate of fire and non-lethal.
spanish.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: An airsoft rifle modified to shoot up to six sedative darts. Magazine fed, featuring a classic blue finish with premium iron sights and a state-of-the-art tracer.
spanish.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: Show them true efficiency with this modern Japanese get-up: the classic black, red and white color scheme with safety glasses, gloves and a communicator is sure to prove how serious you are.
spanish.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
spanish.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: 47 has started his ICA Entrance test by the Tool Shed.
spanish.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
spanish.ui_starting_location_polar_test_gates_de: 47 Has approached the front gate, hidden in shadow.
spanish.APC_desc: 47 has infiltrated the train undetected, now disguised as the Train Conductor, ready to confront the Constant.
spanish.office_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Office Closet for 47 to use.
spanish.workbench_desc: Diana has smuggled a item underneath the weapon workbench for for 47 to use.
spanish.storage_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Storage Car infront of the Ether Lab Car for 47 to use.
spanish.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: Show them all what a high roller you are with this exclusive waistcoat. Features driving gloves, black slacks, shoes and shirt, with a glittering red vest.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: One Elimination type and two Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: Two Elimination types and one Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: Only one Elimination type and Disguise type required for Mission completion.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: No Elimination methods required for Mission completion.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: No Disguises required for Mission completion.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: If 47 is frisked, the Mission will fail.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: Assassinate all Targets, Assassinate all Witnesses and do it all in your suit.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: 47 must steal a semi-auto pistol from a guard.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RAT_DESC: 47 must steal a tube of rat poison.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: 47 must steal a key, a keycard, a security access drive or a RFID chip.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: If any accident kill/pacifcation bodies are found, 47 will have 4 minutes to complete the mission.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: 47 starts the Mission a little buzzed. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: 47 wakes up after drinking too much alcohol. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated. If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated, 47 must not change out of his suit.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: If any shot misses or is not a headshot, the mission will instantly fail. If 47 moves on red, the game will instantly fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: If any shot misses, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: If any shot that hits a npc is not a headshot, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: Do not Eliminate/Pacify when the light is Blue/Red
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: If 47 moves while the light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_TITLE: Do not move when the light is Red
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: If 47 is spotted, any witnesses must be eliminated.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
47 has 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in 47's path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives. A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: If a door is unlocked you will have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: If you Trespass you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: Flamingo suit only, Eliminate all targets, If recorded, evidence must be deleted. Finish Mission in 10 minutes.
spanish.UUI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OBJ_FLAMINGO: Delete evidence from the Hunting Cameras
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: 47 starts visibly armed. 20 Non-targets must be Eliminated, NPCs must stay Alerted and all Targets must be Eliminated. Suit Only.
spanish.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE: The Set Seed field can be used to set the seed for both Roulette modes.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: Complete the Mission in your starting Disguise.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_TITLE: Do not change your starting Disguise
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
No bodies may be found, no non-targets may be Eliminated.
You may not be seen and you must destroy any Surveillance recordings if recorded.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STALKER_OBJ_2: Do not touch the Phantom's Aura
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: Eliminate all Targets by any methods you deem fit.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
If NPCs are not currently Alerted or Panicked, a one minute timer will start.
You must increase tension to stop the timer or fail the mission.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: If NPCs are Alerted or in a Combat Situation, you must de-escalate the situation in 90 seconds or fail the mission.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: If NPCs are Alerted you must de-escalate within 90 seconds
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Complete the mission within 10 minutes, or fail.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: Do not change disguise more than twice.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: Do not change disguise more than twice
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_DESC:
You have 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in your path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_FAIL: Time is relative to the observer. When you're looking down the barrel of a gun time slows down, your whole life flashes by. Stay with it, and you can live a lifetime in that split second.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_DESC: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Guards. Non-Target Civilian Eliminations are allowed.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_TITLE: Do not Eliminate Non Target Guards
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COVERT_ASSASSIN_D: If you are detected you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SLOW_AND_STEADY_D: If you use Agility you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_KIL: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Civilians. Non-Target Guard Eliminations are allowed.
spanish.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_TIT: Do not Eliminate Non Target Civilians

russian.INCLUDE_CONDITIONS_BANNED_IN_ROULETTE_RI: Включить Условия Запрещённые в Roulette Rivals
russian.UI_ROULETTE_PLAYING_CARD_HACKER_DESC: Заострённая игральная карта сделанная на заказ, напоминание о прошлом. Отлично подходит для метания, и для доступа к закрытым зонам.
russian.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DESC: Для поистине разрывной игры в покер. Эта малоприметная покерная фишка обязательно привлечёт чьё-то внимание, и также может быть использована для подрыва дверей. Относительно тихая.
russian.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DETONATOR_DES: Устройство удалённой активации, используется для взрыва Подрывной Покерной Фишки.
russian.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_DESCRIPTION:
Эта опция перегенерирует Случайные Контракты Рулетки со случайным сидом. Контракты Рулетки Трилогии перегенерированы не будут.
ИСПОЛЬЗОВАНИЕ ЭТОЙ ОПЦИИ В КОНТРАКТАХ РУЛЕТКИ ТРИЛОГИИ ВЫЗОВЕТ ОШИБКУ.
russian.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: Золотой вариант особого 5мм пистолета, отлично подходящий для роскошной ночи в казино. Разработанное для предотвращения обнаружения при обыске, это оружие использует боеприпасы пробивающие стены.
russian.firearms_hero_icer_desc: Пистолет под патроны магнум, модифицирован для стрельбы оглушающими патронами. Низкая скорость стрельбы, несмертелен.
russian.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: Страйкбольная винтовка модифицированная под стрельбу седативными дротиками, вплоть до шести. Дротики подаются через магазин, сама винтовка выделяется классической голубой каймой, отличным прицелом и превосходным трассером.
russian.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: Покажите всем подлинную эффективность с этим современным Японским нарядом: классическое сочетание чёрного, красного и белого цветов, вместе с защитными очками и коммуникатором, покажут всем ваши серьёзные намерения.
russian.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: Я уверен что это приведёт к временному парадоксу.
russian.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: Сорок Седьмой начинает свой тест на вступление в МКА у сарая с инструментами.
russian.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: Я уверен что это приведёт к временному парадоксу.
russian.ui_starting_location_polar_test_gates_de: Сорок седьмой подобрался к главным воротам, скрытый в тенях.
russian.APC_desc: Сорок Седьмой проник на поезд незамеченным, замаскированный под проводника, и готовый расправиться с Константой.
russian.office_desc: Диана спрятала предмет для Сорок Седьмого в Офисном шкафу.
russian.workbench_desc: Диана спрятала предмет для Сорок Седьмого под оружейным верстаком.
russian.storage_desc: Диана спрятала предмет для Сорок седьмого в вагоне-хранилище, перед лабораторией Итер.
russian.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: Покажите всем что вы по настоящему крупный игрок с этим особым жилетом. Включает водительские перчатки, туфли и рубашку, с блистающим красным жилетом.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: Одна задача на устранения, и две задачи на маскировки для выполнения миссии.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: Два задачи на устранение, и одна задача на маскировки необходимы для выполнения миссии.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: Только одна задача на устранение, и одна задача на маскировки необходимы для выполнения миссии.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: Задачи связанные с методами устранения отсутствуют.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: Нет обязательных задач на использование маскировок для выполнения миссии.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: Если Сорок Седьмой будет обыскан, задание будет провалено.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: Устраните все цели выстрелами в голову, устраните всех свидетелей, и сделайте это в своём костюме.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_TITLE: Устраните все цели выстрелами в голову
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: Сорок Седьмой должен украсть полуавтоматический пистолет у охранника.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RAT_DESC: Сорок Седьмой должен украсть упаковку крысиного яда.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: Сорок Седьмой должен украсть ключ, устройство доступа охраны, или инфракрасный чип.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: Если тела жертв любого несчастного случая будут найдены, у Сорок Седьмого есть четыре минуты на то, чтобы закончить задание.
Тела жертв несчастных случаев не должны быть обнаружены
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: Сорок Седьмой начнёт задание будучи слегка подвыпившим. [НЕСОВМЕСТИМО С VR]
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: Сорок Седьмой только очнулся после того как слишком много выпил. [НЕСОВМЕСТИМО С VR]
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_VANISHER_DESCRIPT: Все тела должны быть спрятаны в течение 90 секунд.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: Сорок Седьмой начинает в костюме, и ни с чем более. Если Сорок Седьмой устранит персонажа пока горит Синий свет, или усмирит кого-то пока горит красный, задание будет провалено. [НЕСОВМЕСТИМО С VR]
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: Сорок Седьмой начинает в костюме, и ни с чем более. Все цели должны быть устранены, и Сорок Седьмой не должен снимать свой костюм.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: Если любой выстрел не достигает цели, или не является выстрелом в голову, задание считается проваленным. Если Сорок Седьмой движется пока горит красный свет, задание считается проваленным. [НЕСОВМЕСТИМО С VR]
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: Если любой выстрел не попадает в цель, то начинается отсчёт в четыре минуты на выполнение оставшихся задач.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: Если любой выстрел который попадает по персонажу не является выстрелом в голову, то начинается отсчёт в четыре минуты на выполнение оставшихся задач.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: Если Сорок Седьмой устранит персонажа пока горит Синий свет, или усмирит кого-то пока горит Красный, задание будет провалено
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: Не устраняйте/усмиряйте никого пока горит Синий/Красный свет
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: Если Сорок Седьмой движется пока горит красный свет, задание будет провалено. [НЕСОВМЕСТИМО С VR]
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_TITLE: Не двигайтесь пока горит красный свет
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: Если Сорок Седьмой обнаружен, все свидетели должны быть устранены.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
У Сорок Седьмого есть минута на выполнение задания.
Выиграйте время устраняя и усмиряя любого на пути агента.
Чтобы спасти себя, вы должны выполнить все задачи. Опасный Призрак следует за Сорок Седьмым по всему уровню.
Если вы попадёте в зону его Ауры, или попробуете его устранить или усмирить, задание будет немедленно провалено.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: Если любая дверь будет отперта, то начинается отсчёт в четыре минуты на выполнение оставшихся задач.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: Если вы проникните на запретную территорию, то начнётся отсчёт в четыре минуты на выполнение оставшихся задач.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: Только костюм фламинго. Устраните все цели. Если вы были записаны на камеру, улики должны быть стёрты. Задание должно быть закончено за 10 минут.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Мигрируйте на юг в течение десяти минут
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: Сорок Седьмой начинает задание будучи открыто вооружённым. 20 персонажей не являющихся целью должны быть устранены, все персонажи должны оставаться в состоянии тревоги, и все цели должны быть устранены. Только костюм.
russian.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE: Поле "Задайте Сид" может быть использовано для настройки своего сида для обоих режимов рулетки.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: Сорок Седьмой начинает только в своём костюме, и ни с чем более. Все цели должны быть устранены.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: Завершите задание в своей стартовой маскировке.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
Тела должны оставаться не найденными, посторонние не могут быть устранены.
Вас не должны заметить, и любые записанные улики должны быть стёрты.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
Опасный Призрак следует за Сорок Седьмым по всему уровню.
Если вы вступите в зону его ауры, или попытаетесь его устранить или усмирить, задание будет мгновенно провалено.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: Устраните все цели любыми доступными методами.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
Если никто из персонажей не находится в состоянии тревоги или паники, начнётся отсчёт в одну минуту.
Вам необходимо повысить накал страстей, чтобы остановить таймер, или задание будет провалено.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: Если кто-то находится в состоянии тревоги или паники, ситуацию необходимо деэскалировать в течение 90 секунд, или задание будет провалено.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: Если персонажи встревожены, успокойте ситуацию в течение 90 секунд
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Выполните задание за 10 минут, или оно будет провалено.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: Не меняйте маскировку более двух раз.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: Не меняйте маскировку более двух раз
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_DESC:
У вас одна минута на выполнение задания.
Выиграйте немного времени устраняя и усмиряя любого на вашем пути.
Чтобы спастись, вам необходимо выполнить все остальные задачи.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_FAIL: Время относительно для наблюдателя. Когда ты смотришь в дуло ствола, время замедляется. Вся жизнь проносится перед глазами. Замри, и ты сможешь прожить целую жизнь в эту долю секунды.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_DESC: Не устраняйте охранников не являющихся целью. Устранение сторонних гражданских разрешено.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_TITLE: Не устраняйте охранников не являющихся целями
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COVERT_ASSASSIN_D: Если вас обнаружат, у вас будет четыре минуты на завершение всех задач.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SLOW_AND_STEADY_D: Если вы будете использовать приёмы ловкости, начнётся отсчёт в четыре минуты на выполнение осташихся задач.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_KIL: Не устранять гражданских не являющихся целью. Устранение охранников не целей разрешено.
russian.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_TIT: Не устраняйте гражданских не являющихся целью

chineseSimplified.UI_ROULETTE_PLAYING_CARD_HACKER_DESC: 一张磨得锋利的定制扑克牌，上面印有对过去的回忆。非常适合投掷和进入禁区。
chineseSimplified.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DESC: 为扑克牌游戏增添火药味。这种不起眼的扑克牌筹码一定会引起人们的注意，还可以遥控引爆，把门炸开。相对安静。
chineseSimplified.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DETONATOR_DES: 一个遥控触发装置，用于引爆爆炸扑克筹码。
chineseSimplified.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_DESCRIPTION:
这将使用随机种子重新生成随机轮盘赌契约。
在三部曲轮盘赌契约中使用会导致错误。
chineseSimplified.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_TITLE: 重新生成随机轮盘赌契约吗？
chineseSimplified.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: 定制5mm手枪的金色变体，适合在赌场度过迷人的光辉夜晚。此武器使用穿墙弹，可穿过防弹玻璃。
chineseSimplified.UI_CHALLENGES_GLOBAL_ROULETTE_CHALLENGE_: 完成1次每日轮盘赌契约。
完成2次每日轮盘赌契约。
完成3次每日轮盘赌契约。
chineseSimplified.UI_MENU_PAGE_REGEN_CONTRACTS: 重新生成随机轮盘赌契约
chineseSimplified.firearms_hero_icer_desc: 经过改装的马格南手枪，可发射瞬时震荡弹。射速低，不致命。
chineseSimplified.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: 经过改装的气枪，最多可发射六枚镇静剂飞镖。由弹夹供弹，采用经典的蓝色漆面，配备优质铁制瞄准镜和最先进的追踪器。
chineseSimplified.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: 用这套现代日式装扮向他们展示真正的效率吧：经典的黑、红、白三色混搭，配上安全眼镜、手套和通讯器，一定能证明你是多么严肃认真。
chineseSimplified.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: 我很肯定这会造成时间上的矛盾。
chineseSimplified.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: 47在工具间开始了他的ICA入门测试。
chineseSimplified.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: 我很肯定这会造成时间上的矛盾。
chineseSimplified.APC_desc: 47已悄无声息地潜入列车，现在伪装成了列车长，准备与“永恒常量”对峙。
chineseSimplified.office_desc: 戴安娜在办公室壁橱里偷运了一件物品供47使用。
chineseSimplified.workbench_desc: 戴安娜在武器工作台下偷运了一件物品供47使用。
chineseSimplified.storage_desc: 戴安娜在苍穹实验室车厢前的储藏车厢里偷运了一件物品供47使用。
chineseSimplified.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: 穿上这款独特的马甲，向他们展示你有多么高贵。配有驾驶手套、黑色休闲裤、皮鞋和衬衫，以及闪闪发光的红色背心。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: 完成此任务需要完成一个消灭型目标和两个伪装型目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: 完成此任务完成需要两个消灭型目标和一个伪装型目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: 完成此任务只需一种消灭型和一种伪装型目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: 完成此任务无需消灭型。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: 完成此任务无需伪装型。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: 如果47被搜身，任务将失败。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: 以爆头方式刺杀所有目标，消灭所有目击者，并穿着你的西装完成一切。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_TITLE: 以爆头方式刺杀所有目标
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: 47必须从警卫处偷得一把半自动手枪。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: 47必须偷取钥匙、钥匙卡、安全访问驱动器或RFID芯片。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: 如果任何意外死亡或制伏的尸体被发现，47将有4分钟时间完成任务。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: 47开始任务时有点嗡嗡作响。[不兼容VR]
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: 47在喝了太多酒后徐徐醒来。[不兼容VR]
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: 47只穿着他的西装开始任务。必须消灭所有目标。如果47在蓝灯亮起时消灭了NPC或在红灯亮起时制伏了NPC，则任务失败。[不兼容VR]
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: 47只穿着他的西装开始任务。必须消灭所有目标，而47不能换下西装。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: 如果射弹未击中或未爆头，任务将立即失败。如果红灯时47移动，游戏将立即失败。[不兼容VR]
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: 如果射弹未击中，你只剩4分钟完成所有目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: 如果你击中NPC但没有爆头，你只剩4分钟完成所有目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: 如果47在蓝灯亮起时消灭NPC或在红灯亮起时制伏NPC，任务将失败。[不兼容VR]
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: 当灯光为蓝/红色时不要消灭/制伏
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: 如果47在红灯亮起时移动，任务将失败。[不兼容VR]
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: 如果47被发现，则必须消灭所有目击者。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
47有1分钟的时间来完成任务。
通过制伏和消灭47路上的任何人来争取更多时间。
要拯救自己，你必须完成所有其他目标。一个危险的魅影在整个关卡中跟踪47。
如果你踏入它的光环或试图消灭或制伏它，任务将立即失败。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: 如果门被解锁，你将有4分钟时间完成所有目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: 如果你非法入侵，你将有4分钟时间完成所有目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PLACATION_DESC: 不被发现的情况下制伏三名NPC。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PLACATION_TITLE: 不被发现的情况下制伏三名NPC
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: 仅限火烈鸟套装。消灭所有目标。如果被记录，必须删除证据。在10分钟内完成任务。
chineseSimplified.UUI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OBJ_FLAMINGO: 删除狩猎摄像机中的证据
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: 47以明显武装开始任务。必须消灭20名非目标。NPC必须保持警惕。必须消灭所有目标。只穿西装。
chineseSimplified.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE: 设置种子字段可用于设置两种轮盘赌模式的种子。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: 47只穿西装开始任务。必须消灭所有目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: 穿着你开始时的伪装完成任务。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_TITLE: 不要改变开始时的伪装。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
不得发现尸体，不得消灭非目标。
不得被发现，并且必须销毁所有已记录的监控录像。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
一个危险的魅影在整个关卡中潜行追随着47。
如果你进入它的光环或试图消灭或制伏它，任务将立即失败。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: 使用你认为合适的任何方法消灭所有目标。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
如果NPC当前未处于警觉或恐慌状态，则会启动一分钟计时器。
你必须增加紧张程度来停止计时器，否则任务失败。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: 如果NPC收到警报或处于战斗状态，你必须在90秒内缓和局势，否则任务失败。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: 如果NPC收到警报，你必须在90秒内缓和局势
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: 在10分钟内完成任务，否则失败。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: 不要更换伪装超过两次。
chineseSimplified.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: 不要更换伪装超过两次

你有1分钟的时间来完成任务。
通过制伏和消灭任何挡路的人来争取更多时间。

chineseTraditional.UI_ROULETTE_PLAYING_CARD_HACKER_DESC: 一張削尖的訂製撲克牌，上面刻著過去的痕跡。非常適合投擲和進入禁區。
chineseTraditional.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DESC: 玩一場激烈的撲克遊戲。這種不起眼的撲克籌碼肯定會吸引人們的注意，並且可以遠端引爆來炸開門。比較安靜。
chineseTraditional.UI_ROULETTE_BREACHING_CHIP_DETONATOR_DES: 遠端觸發裝置，用於引爆爆炸性撲克籌碼。
chineseTraditional.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_DESCRIPTION:
這將使用隨機種子重新產生隨機輪盤合約。這不會重新產生三部曲輪盤合約。
在三部曲輪盤合約中使用此功能將導致錯誤。
chineseTraditional.UI_DIALOG_RESET_BULLETDANCER_TITLE: 重新產生隨機輪盤合約？
chineseTraditional.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: Custom 5mm 的金色款式適合賭場的迷人夜晚。這種武器專為透過搜身而設計，使用穿牆彈藥。
chineseTraditional.UI_CHALLENGES_GLOBAL_ROULETTE_CHALLENGE_: 完成 1 份每日輪盤契約。
完成 2 份每日輪盤契約。
完成 3 份每日輪盤契約。
chineseTraditional.UI_MENU_PAGE_REGEN_CONTRACTS: 重新產生隨機輪盤契約
chineseTraditional.firearms_hero_icer_desc: 一把改裝的馬格南手槍，可發射瞬發震盪彈。射速低，不致命。
chineseTraditional.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: 一把經過改裝的軟氣槍，可發射多達六支鎮靜飛鏢。採用彈匣供彈，經典藍色塗裝，配備優質機械瞄具和先進的曳光彈。
chineseTraditional.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: 透過這款現代日式服裝向他們展示真正的效率吧：經典的黑紅白三色配色方案，搭配安全眼鏡、手套和通訊器，一定能證明您有多認真。
chineseTraditional.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: 我確信這會導致時間悖論。
chineseTraditional.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: 47 已在工具棚開始他的 ICA 入學考試。
chineseTraditional.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: 我確信這會導致時間悖論。
chineseTraditional.ui_starting_location_polar_test_gates_de: 47 已經接近前門，隱藏在陰影中。
chineseTraditional.APC_desc: 47 已悄悄潛入火車，現已偽裝成列車長，準備與常任對峙。
chineseTraditional.office_desc: 戴安娜偷偷將一件物品帶進辦公室壁櫥供 47 使用。
chineseTraditional.workbench_desc: 戴安娜在武器工作台下面偷偷藏了一件可供 47 使用的物品。
chineseTraditional.storage_desc: 黛安娜將一件物品偷運到乙太實驗室車前面的儲物車中，供 47 使用。
chineseTraditional.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: 穿上這件專屬背心，向大家展示你有多熱愛賭博。內含駕駛手套、黑色休閒褲、鞋子和襯衫，以及閃亮的紅色背心。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: 完成任務需要一個消滅類型目標和兩個偽裝類型目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: 完成任務需要兩個消滅類型目標和一個偽裝類型目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: 完成任務需要一個消滅類型目標和一個偽裝類型目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: 完成任務不需要消滅方法。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: 完成任務不需要偽裝方法。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: 如果 47 被搜身，任務就會失敗。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: 用爆頭殺死所有目標，消滅所有目擊者，並一直穿著你的西服。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: 47 必須從警衛那裡偷一​​把半自動手槍。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: 47 必須偷一把鑰匙、一張鑰匙卡、一個安全門禁驅動器或一個 RFID 晶片。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: 如果發現任何意外死亡/擊暈屍體，47 將有 4 分鐘的時間完成任務。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: 47 開始任務時有點暈。 [不支援VR]
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: 47 喝多了酒後醒來。 [不支援 VR]
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_VANISHER_DESCRIPT: 在 90 秒內隱藏所有屍體。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: 47 只穿西裝開始任務。所有目標必須被消滅。如果 47 在藍燈亮時消滅 NPC，或在紅燈亮時擊暈 NPC，任務將會失敗。 [不支援 VR]
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: 47 只穿西裝開始任務。所有目標必須消除，且 47 不得更換西裝。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: 如果任何一槍未命中或未擊中頭部，任務將立即失敗。如果紅燈亮起時 47 移動，遊戲將立即失敗。 [不支援VR]
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: 如果任何一槍失敗，則只剩下四分鐘的時間來完成所有目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: 如果擊中 NPC 的任何一槍不是爆頭，則只剩下四分鐘的時間來完成所有目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: 如果 47 在藍燈亮時消滅 NPC，或在紅燈亮時擊暈 NPC，任務將會失敗。 [不支援 VR]
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: 當燈光為藍色/紅色時，請勿消滅/擊暈
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: 如果 47 在紅燈亮時移動，任務將會失敗。 [不支援 VR]
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: 如果發現 47，則必須消滅所有目擊者。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
47 有 1 分鐘的時間完成任務。
擊暈並消滅 47 路上的任何人，以爭取更多時間。
為了自救，你必須完成所有其他目標。一個危險的幽靈正在關卡中追蹤 47。
如果你踏入它的光環，或試圖消滅或擊暈它，你的任務將立即失敗。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: 如果門解鎖，您將有 4 分鐘的時間來完成所有目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: 如果您非法侵入，您有 4 分鐘的時間來完成所有目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PLACATION_DESC: 悄無聲息地安撫三名 NPC。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PLACATION_TITLE: 悄無聲息地安撫三名 NPC
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: 僅限火烈鳥套裝，消滅所有目標，如果記錄下來，則必須刪除證據。 10分鐘內完成任務。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: 47 開始明顯武裝起來。必須消滅 20 個非目標，NPC 必須保持警覺，並且必須消滅所有目標。僅限西裝。
chineseTraditional.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE: 設定種子欄位可用於設定兩種輪盤模式的種子。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: 47 一開始只剩下他的西裝。所有目標都必須被消滅。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: 以你最初的偽裝完成任務。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_TITLE: 不要改變你的起始偽裝
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
不得發現屍體，不得消滅非目標。
不得被發現，並且必須銷毀任何已記錄的監視器錄影。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
一個危險的幽靈在關卡中潛行 47。
如果你進入它的氣場或試圖消滅或擊暈它，你的任務將立即失敗。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: 使用您認為合適的任何方法消滅所有目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
如果 NPC 目前未處於警覺或恐慌狀態，則會啟動一分鐘計時器。
您必須增加緊張程度才能停止計時器，否則任務失敗。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: 如果 NPC 處於警戒狀態或戰鬥狀態，您必須在 90 秒內緩和局勢，否則任務失敗。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: 如果 NPC 處於警戒狀態，你必須在 90 秒內降級
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: 改變偽裝的次數不得超過兩次。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: 改變偽裝的次數不得超過兩次
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_DESC:
您有 1 分鐘的時間來完成任務。
擊暈並消滅任何擋路的人，以爭取更多時間。
為了自救，您必須完成所有其他目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_FAIL: 時間與觀察者息息相關。當你注視著槍管時，時間彷彿慢了下來，你的一生彷彿一閃而過。堅持下去，你就能在那一瞬間擁有一輩子。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_DESC: 請勿消滅非目標警衛。允許消滅非目標平民。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COVERT_ASSASSIN_D: 如果被發現，您有 4 分鐘的時間來完成所有目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SLOW_AND_STEADY_D: 如果您使用敏捷，您有 4 分鐘的時間來完成所有目標。
chineseTraditional.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_KIL: 請勿消滅非目標平民。允許消滅非目標守衛。

USING THIS IN A TRILOGY ROULETTE CONTRACT WILL CAUSE AN ERROR.
japanese.ui_firearms_hero_pistol_ultralight_golde: A golden variant of the Custom 5mm fit for a glamorous night at the casino. Designed to pass through frisks, this weapon utilizes wall-piercing ammunition.
japanese.firearms_hero_icer_desc: A magnum pistol modified to shoot Instant Concussion Rounds. Low rate of fire and non-lethal.
japanese.UI_ROULETTE_DART_RIFLE_DESC: An airsoft rifle modified to shoot up to six sedative darts. Magazine fed, featuring a classic blue finish with premium iron sights and a state-of-the-art tracer.
japanese.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_DAILY_ROULETTE_SUIT: Show them true efficiency with this modern Japanese get-up: the classic black, red and white color scheme with safety glasses, gloves and a communicator is sure to prove how serious you are.
japanese.ui_starting_location_scaffolding_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
japanese.ui_starting_location_polar_abandoned_she: 47 has started his ICA Entrance test by the Tool Shed.
japanese.ui_starting_location_checkpoint_desc: I'm pretty sure this causes a time paradox.
japanese.ui_starting_location_polar_test_gates_de: 47 Has approached the front gate, hidden in shadow.
japanese.APC_desc: 47 has infiltrated the train undetected, now disguised as the Train Conductor, ready to confront the Constant.
japanese.office_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Office Closet for 47 to use.
japanese.workbench_desc: Diana has smuggled a item underneath the weapon workbench for for 47 to use.
japanese.storage_desc: Diana has smuggled a item into the Storage Car infront of the Ether Lab Car for 47 to use.
japanese.UI_TOKEN_OUTFIT_HERO_MONTE_CARLO_DESC: Show them all what a high roller you are with this exclusive waistcoat. Features driving gloves, black slacks, shoes and shirt, with a glittering red vest.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_1TO2_DESC: One Elimination type and two Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_2TO1_DESC: Two Elimination types and one Disguise type Objectives required for Mission completion.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_BOGO_DESC: Only one Elimination type and Disguise type required for Mission completion.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_K_DESC: No Elimination methods required for Mission completion.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREE_D_DESC: No Disguises required for Mission completion.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FRISKY_BUISNESS_D: If 47 is frisked, the Mission will fail.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_WICK_DESC: Assassinate all Targets, Assassinate all Witnesses and do it all in your suit.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STEALPISTOL_DESC: 47 must steal a semi-auto pistol from a guard.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RAT_DESC: 47 must steal a tube of rat poison.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TONY_DESC: 47 must steal a key, a keycard, a security access drive or a RFID chip.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOHAPPYACCIDENTS_: If any accident kill/pacifcation bodies are found, 47 will have 4 minutes to complete the mission.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BUZZED_DESC: 47 starts the Mission a little buzzed. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BENDER_DESC: 47 wakes up after drinking too much alcohol. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPRB_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated. If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSPSO_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated, 47 must not change out of his suit.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BOS_DESCRIPTION: If any shot misses or is not a headshot, the mission will instantly fail. If 47 moves on red, the game will instantly fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NOMISSES_DESCRIPT: If any shot misses, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BULLSEYE_DESCRIPT: If any shot that hits a npc is not a headshot, there will only be four minutes left to complete all Objectives.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_DESCRIPTION: If 47 Eliminates a NPC while the light is Blue or Pacifies a NPC while the Light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RB_TITLE: Do not Eliminate/Pacify when the light is Blue/Red
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_DESCRIPTION: If 47 moves while the light is Red, the Mission will fail. [NOT VR COMPATIBLE]
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_RGY_TITLE: Do not move when the light is Red
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SEENOEVIL_DESCRIP: If 47 is spotted, any witnesses must be eliminated.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_MINUTE_DESC:
47 has 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in 47's path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives. A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HECATE_DESCRIPTIO: If a door is unlocked you will have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PRIVATE_PROPERTY_: If you Trespass you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_BIRDPERCENT_DESC: Flamingo suit only, Eliminate all targets, If recorded, evidence must be deleted. Finish Mission in 10 minutes.
japanese.UUI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OBJ_FLAMINGO: Delete evidence from the Hunting Cameras
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_TERRORIST_DESC: 47 starts visibly armed. 20 Non-targets must be Eliminated, NPCs must stay Alerted and all Targets must be Eliminated. Suit Only.
japanese.UI_DIALOG_CONTRACT_TEXT_ROULETTE_HELP_TE: The Set Seed field can be used to set the seed for both Roulette modes.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_OSP_DESC: 47 starts with nothing but his suit. All targets must be eliminated.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_DESC: Complete the Mission in your starting Disguise.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_IMMUTABLE_TITLE: Do not change your starting Disguise
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_PERFECTIONIST_DES:
No bodies may be found, no non-targets may be Eliminated.
You may not be seen and you must destroy any Surveillance recordings if recorded.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_STALKER_DESC:
A dangerous Phantom stalks 47 across the level.
If you step into its Aura or attempt to Eliminate or Pacify it, you will instantly fail the mission.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_STALKER_OBJ_2: Do not touch the Phantom's Aura
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_FREEBIE_DESC: Eliminate all Targets by any methods you deem fit.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_HEAT_DESC:
If NPCs are not currently Alerted or Panicked, a one minute timer will start.
You must increase tension to stop the timer or fail the mission.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_DESC: If NPCs are Alerted or in a Combat Situation, you must de-escalate the situation in 90 seconds or fail the mission.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_MOOD_KILLER_TITLE: If NPCs are Alerted you must de-escalate within 90 seconds
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COMPLETE_MISSION_: Complete the mission within 10 minutes, or fail.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_DESC: Do not change disguise more than twice.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_DUOTONE_TITLE: Do not change disguise more than twice
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_DESC:
You have 1 minute to complete the mission.
Buy some more time by pacifying and eliminating anyone who is in your path.
To save yourself, you must complete all other Objectives.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_ICA_MINUTE_FAIL: Time is relative to the observer. When you're looking down the barrel of a gun time slows down, your whole life flashes by. Stay with it, and you can live a lifetime in that split second.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_DESC: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Guards. Non-Target Civilian Eliminations are allowed.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_GUARDS_TITLE: Do not Eliminate Non Target Guards
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_COVERT_ASSASSIN_D: If you are detected you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_SLOW_AND_STEADY_D: If you use Agility you have 4 minutes to complete all Objectives.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_KIL: Do not Eliminate Non-Target Civilians. Non-Target Guard Eliminations are allowed.
japanese.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GLOBAL_NO_NON_TARGET_TIT: Do not Eliminate Non Target Civilians
